<Link id="l00508" /><CodeLine lineNumber="508"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// This interface is used to plug different priorities computation</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00513" /><CodeLine lineNumber="513"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// decide.</span></CodeLine>
